description:
I was looking for the CS Source Beta online, but could never find it. Recently, I heard the retail box of CSS contains the oldest build you can get. So, I ripped
it and made a few modifications to make it like the CS Beta. I included the GCF files in case the game gets messed up, but it runs stable.

